title: Summoners Society
body:
Hello Summoners,

We are a facebook group that is for OCE summoners! We run 3 online events a month and lots of community games on discord! 

So make sure to come check out the facebook group and discord for future events and to meet awesome Summoners! 
https://discord.gg/3zGt6Ya
